name: Embrace Life
description: I'm humbled that my dear friend, one of my mentors on how to live life full and right, was willing to pose for me and show her ability to embrace life fully, no restraints. In her own words "onward and forward Kitty." Thank you V, for giving me the opportunity to show the world how I see you. A beautiful force of nature, not restrained by social standards and stale views. I can only hope I'm doing you justice.
